      "content": "it's just weird because my lights have been acting super strange lately. like, whenever i'm stressed or angry, they seem to dim or change color in a way that feels... intentional. like they're reacting to me. if they're actually doing this to gather data on my moods, how would they even hide that from the user? it feels like they're just testing the algorithms on us.",
